                            <li><i class="fas fa-passport"></i> Identity Proof (Aadhaar/Driving License/Passport)</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Address Proof of Partners (Bank Statement/Utility Bill)</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-building"></i> Registered Office Address Proof (Electricity/Gas Bill, NOC from Landlord)</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-portrait"></i> Latest Passport-size photographs</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-envelope-open-text"></i> Valid Email IDs and Mobile Numbers</li>
                        </ul>
